<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lạ fjr bʿdhạ ylwḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lạ fjr bʿdhạ ylwḥ wlạ qlby bsrh ybwḥ fy ʿdẖạby bạlḥb wynwḥ dmwʿy ṭwfạn
 tflk yạ nwḥ ʿṭsẖy fy ạlʿsẖq lạ ynthy wạljmạl mn
 ḥwly lạ ạ̉sẖthy wạ̉nạ bạlwḥdẗ mbtly wḥwạsy tfyḍ wlạ
 tnjly yạ ạ̹lh ạlḥb ạ̉ṣgẖy ạ̹ly mn mnh ʿly wʿly̱
 hly dmwʿy ṭwfạn</lyrics>
<hymn_number>7977</hymn_number>
<author>nzạr fạrs, nzạr fạrs</author>
</song>